column5: The time is almost here. Heading out early in the morning for a week at Lake Biscotatsi fishing for eyes and pike, then it is off to Lake Nipigon in prusuit of giant Specks, Lakers and Pike. Ill take lots of pictures and will hopefully have agreat few posts when I return!   Darren
Have a great trip. What am I saying....how could you not have a good trip with those waters. Drive safe.
Have a great time Darren.  Go catch lots  How's the finger mending?  Joey
always wanted to fish Biscotasi but I turn right at 560..I need to turn left and give it a try   good luck
Good luck Darren, have a great time bud!!
Good Luck Bucktail.. I'll be on lake bisco for a week in August. Let us all know how you make out.

Have a great couple of trips Bucktail, and be safe.  When will you be driving up to Nipigon? Sounds like I will be driving back to TBay near the same time as you, as I will be at Lakair, this year, then starting the drive home on the 24th of June.
Heading to Nipigon on the 22nd and coming back on the 1st.  Team 7 is going to have a few nice entries ;-)
